CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Icahn Enterprises LP is a provider of diversified business services in the United States. The company operates its business through varied segments which include Investment, Automotive, Energy, Food Packaging, Real Estate, Pharma, and Home Fashion. Among these, the Energy segment derives maximum revenue from the company. Geographically, it generates maximum revenue from the United States.
